data.title: Hotham Park, Arun District Podcast
data.meta_description: In the coastal town of Bognor Regis, in the county of West Sussex in England, lies the public park Hotham Park. Founded by Sir Richard Hotham, who also gave his name to the city, the park houses the historic Hotham Park House, built in 1792 and still standing today. Opened to the public in 1947, ...
